<div class="K2FeedIntroText"><p><img src="http://sports.ndtv.com/images/stories/euroloew12090.jpg" border="0" align="left" />Loew's Germany are five-points clear at the top of Group C, with Austria second on goal difference.</p></div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/NdtvSports-allsports/~4/sTWk8WDdz-g" height="1" width="1"/>
