<div class="K2FeedIntroText"><p><img src="http://sports.ndtv.com/images/stories/benjohnson_120.jpg" border="0" align="left" />Johnson said he decided to speak out because he wanted to help make changes in today's society about drugs in sports.</p></div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/NdtvSports-allsports/~4/9UwHBNcceDE" height="1" width="1"/>
