<span>published on Thu, 05 Sep 2013 07:48:10 +0000</span><br />
<div class="K2FeedIntroText"><p><img src="http://sports.ndtv.com/images/stories/redbull120-sgp.jpg" border="0" align="left" />After the Milton Keynes-based outfit confirmed this week that Australian Daniel Ricciardo will line-up alongside defending triple champion German Sebastian Vettel next year, Newey said that he was particularly eager to bring on a driver for the long term.</p></div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/NdtvSports-allsports/~4/apUzEoVxHZs" height="1" width="1"/>
<li><a href='http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/NdtvSports-allsports/~3/SAjrJ8lX8JI/213547-force-india-chief-vijay-mallya-warns-against-pay-drivers'>Force India chief Vijay Mallya warns against pay drivers</a><br />
<span>published on Thu, 05 Sep 2013 07:41:16 +0000</span><br />
<div class="K2FeedIntroText"><p><img src="http://sports.ndtv.com/images/stories/mallyaform120.jpg" border="0" align="left" />The co-owner of the Silverstone-based outfit says he does not believe in recruiting drivers purely based on what kind of budget they can bring the team in advertising revenue.</p></div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/NdtvSports-allsports/~4/SAjrJ8lX8JI" height="1" width="1"/>
