<span>published on Thu, 05 Sep 2013 07:33:29 +0000</span><br />
<div class="K2FeedIntroText"><p><img src="http://sports.ndtv.com/images/stories/hamilton_chinesegp-120.jpg" border="0" align="left" />The 28-year-old Briton may trail leader and defending triple world champion German Sebastian Vettel in this year's title race, but his speed and form has kept alive his belief that he can mount a late challenge.</p></div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/NdtvSports-allsports/~4/fw6IQCrZaDU" height="1" width="1"/>
