<span>published on Thu, 05 Sep 2013 07:15:49 +0000</span><br />
<div class="K2FeedIntroText"><p><img src="http://sports.ndtv.com/images/stories/17052011/gasquet120.jpg" border="0" align="left" />Gasquet, who is a close friend of the world number two, recalled how he defeated Nadal at the Les Petits As junior event in the French city of Tarbes when they were both just 13.</p></div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/NdtvSports-allsports/~4/qnOfHa5--rI" height="1" width="1"/>
<li><a href='http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/NdtvSports-allsports/~3/g2_rrrbP7Dw/213542-us-open-victoria-azarenka-books-semis-against-flavia-pennetta'>US Open: Victoria Azarenka books semis against Flavia Pennetta</a><br />
<span>published on Thu, 05 Sep 2013 05:24:19 +0000</span><br />
<div class="K2FeedIntroText"><p><img src="http://sports.ndtv.com/images/stories/azarenka_carlsbad12090.jpg" border="0" align="left" />The 24-year-old second-seed Azarenka from Belarus took only 76 minutes to defeat the 48th-ranked Slovakian while 83rd-rated Pennetta reached her first Grand Slam last four by ousting 10th-seeded compatriot Roberta Vinci 6-4, 6-1.</p></div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/NdtvSports-allsports/~4/g2_rrrbP7Dw" height="1" width="1"/>
<li><a href='http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/NdtvSports-allsports/~3/WR3HR1_NilM/213541-international-olympics-committee-continues-to-keep-india-out-of-olympics-fold'>International Olympic Committee refuses to admit India into its fold</a><br />
<span>published on Thu, 05 Sep 2013 04:45:05 +0000</span><br />
<div class="K2FeedIntroText"><p><img src="http://sports.ndtv.com/images/stories/ioa_oly_120.jpg" border="0" align="left" />The executive body of the International Olympic Committee wants Indian Olympic Association to modify constitution and accept "charge-sheet" clause for good governance. India remain defiant as IOA vice-president Tarlochan Singh says charge-sheet clause was an ordinary issue and no amendment was possible without general body's approval.</p></div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/NdtvSports-allsports/~4/WR3HR1_NilM" height="1" width="1"/>
